---
config:
  theme: redux
---
flowchart TD
    A1[HealthTech_PatientRecords] --> A[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]
    A --> B[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    B -- Memory read successful --> C[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
    B -- Memory access error --> D[HealthTech_PatientRecords]
    D --> E[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    E --> F[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]
    C --> G{HealthTech_PatientRecords}
    G -- Yes --> H[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    G -- No --> I[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]
    I --> J[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]
    J --> K[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]
    K --> A
    H --> L{HealthTech_LabAnalyzer}
    L -- Immediate, Implied, Accumulator --> M[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]
    L -- Zero Page, Indexed, Absolute --> N[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    L -- Indirect, Relative --> O[HealthTech_PatientRecords]
    M --> P[HealthTech_PatientRecords]
    N --> Q[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    O --> R[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
    P --> S[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    Q --> S
    R --> S
    S --> T{HealthTech_PatientRecords}
    T -- "Arithmetic/Logical - e.g., ADC, AND" --> U[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
    T -- "Load/Store - e.g., LDA, STA" --> V[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    T -- "Branch - e.g., BEQ, JMP" --> W[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]
    T -- "Stack - e.g., PHA, RTS" --> X[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    T -- "System - e.g., BRK, RTI" --> Y[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    U --> Z[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]
    V --> Z
    W --> AA[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]
    X --> Z
    Y --> AB[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]
    AA -- Met --> AC[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
    AA --  Not mett --> AD[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    AC --> Z
    AD --> Z
    AB -- Interrupt triggered --> AE[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    AB -- Return from interrupt --> AF[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]
    AE --> AG[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
    AF --> Z
    Z --> AH[HealthTech_PatientRecords]
    AG --> AH
    AH --> AI{HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault}
    AI -- "NMI pending - e.g., PPU VBlank" --> AJ[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]
    AI -- "IRQ pending - e.g., mapper, APU" --> AK[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
    AI -- No interrupts --> AL[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
    AJ --> AM[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
    AK --> AN[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]
    AL --> AO[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
    AM --> AO
    AN --> AO
    AO --> AP{HealthTech_EMR_Sync}
    AP -- Yes --> AQ[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    AQ --> AR[HealthTech_PatientRecords]
    AR --> AS[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
    AS --> AT[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    AT --> AU[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]
    AP -- No --> AU
    AU --> A
    style AI stroke:#000000
